@NODE "Introduction" "Introduction"

 @{FG SHINE}@{U}Introduction@{UU}:@{FG TEXT}

   HereticPortal is a GUI for Heretic (Amiga port) It has many nice features,
   such as:
   @{B}·@{UB} Good looking MUI interface. (Using MUIRexx!)
   @{B}·@{UB} It's small.
   @{B}·@{UB} It's very easy to use.
@ENDNODE

